changerating-error-invalid-rating: {{doc-apierror}} Also used by the Special:ChangeRating page if the user tries to submit a tampered form which contains a codename that isn't recognized nor registered as a valid codename (codenames and other rating logic are set up in MediaWiki:Are-ratings)
changerating-error-no-changes-requested: Error message shown on Special:ChangeRating if the user tries to give the page the same rating it already has
changerating-nolog-text: A hint message for no result
